title: Keeping Up with the Kardashians: Season Six
description: All 16 episodes from the sixth season of the American TV reality show centred around the day-to-day lives of the Los Angeles celebrity family. The episodes comprise: 'Family Vs. Money', 'Kim Becomes a Stage Mom', 'The Former Mrs. Jenner', 'Out of Wedlock', 'Thicker Than Water', 'Kendall Goes On Birth Control', 'The Haves and the Have Nots', 'What Happens in Vegas, Stays in Vegas', 'Talk to My Agent', 'The Family Vacation', 'Getting to Know You', 'Trouble in Paradise', 'The Proposal', 'Kim's Fairytale Wedding: A Kardashian Event - Part One', 'Kim's Fairytale Wedding: A Kardashian Event - Part Two' and 'Kendall's Sweet 16'.
